headline: Wall Street Lunch: OpenAI To Develop LLM 'Garlic' To Counter Google's AI Gains
summary: OpenAI (OPENAI) is developing a large language model called Garlic to counter Google's (GOOG) (GOOGL) recent gains in AI development, according to The Information.

headline: Is Monster Beverage Stock Outperforming the Dow?
summary: Soft drinks giant Monster Beverage has significantly outperformed the Dow over the past year, and analysts remain bullish on the stock’s prospects.
